				GWM PLANNED ENHANCEMENTS:
				#########################

This is the list of the things we are adding, or planning to add, to GWM/WOOL.
Mail us your wishes if they are not already on this list.

				#########################

Selection support

Generic handling of property and selection contents

send/receive ClientMessage

I/O redirection

Xerox ROOMS profile

timeout

more drawing primitives in pixmaps

more debugging aids

dynamically add/replace/remove a son of a menu or bar.

hooks in wobs for move/resize/restack

Object-oriented extensions to WOOL (classes, objects, methods)

